#: ../../source/reference/dataframe/generated/maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.nsmallest.rst:2
msgid "maxframe.dataframe.DataFrame.nsmallest"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.df_nsmallest:1 of
msgid "Return the first `n` rows ordered by `columns` in ascending order."
msgstr "返回按 `columns` 升序排列的前 `n` 行。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.df_nsmallest:3 of
msgid ""
"Return the first `n` rows with the smallest values in `columns`, in "
"ascending order. The columns that are not specified are returned as well,"
" but not used for ordering."
msgstr ""
"返回 `columns` 中值最小的前 `n` 行，按升序排列。未指定的列也会返回，但不"
"用于排序。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.df_nsmallest:7 of
msgid ""
"This method is equivalent to ``df.sort_values(columns, "
"ascending=True).head(n)``, but more performant."
msgstr ""
"此方法等价于 ``df.sort_values(columns, ascending=True).head(n)``，但性能"
"更优。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.df_nsmallest of
msgid "参数"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.df_nsmallest:11 of
msgid "Number of items to retrieve."
msgstr "要检索的项目数量。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.df_nsmallest:13 of
msgid "Column name or names to order by."
msgstr "用于排序的列名或列名列表。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.df_nsmallest:15 of
msgid ""
"Where there are duplicate values:  - ``first`` : take the first "
"occurrence. - ``last`` : take the last occurrence. - ``all`` : do not "
"drop any duplicates, even it means   selecting more than `n` items."
msgstr ""
"当存在重复值时：  - ``first`` : 取首次出现的。 - ``last`` : 取最后出现的"
"。 - ``all`` : 不删除任何重复项，即使这意味着选择超过 `n` 项。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.df_nsmallest:15 of
msgid "Where there are duplicate values:"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.df_nsmallest:17 of
msgid "``first`` : take the first occurrence."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.df_nsmallest:18 of
msgid "``last`` : take the last occurrence."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.df_nsmallest:19 of
msgid ""
"``all`` : do not drop any duplicates, even it means selecting more than "
"`n` items."
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.df_nsmallest of
msgid "返回类型"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.df_nsmallest:27 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.nlargest`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.df_nsmallest:28 of
msgid "Return the first `n` rows ordered by `columns` in descending order."
msgstr "返回按 `columns` 降序排列的前 `n` 行。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.df_nsmallest:30 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.sort_values`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.df_nsmallest:31 of
msgid "Sort DataFrame by the values."
msgstr "按值对 DataFrame 进行排序。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.df_nsmallest:33 of
msgid ":py:obj:`DataFrame.head`"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.df_nsmallest:34 of
msgid "Return the first `n` rows without re-ordering."
msgstr "返回前 `n` 行而不重新排序。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.df_nsmallest:37 of
msgid "示例"
msgstr ""

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.df_nsmallest:61 of
msgid ""
"In the following example, we will use ``nsmallest`` to select the three "
"rows having the smallest values in column \"population\"."
msgstr ""
"在下面的示例中，我们将使用 ``nsmallest`` 来选择 \"population\" 列中值最小"
"的三行。"

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.df_nsmallest:70 of
msgid "When using ``keep='last'``, ties are resolved in reverse order:"
msgstr "当使用 ``keep='last'`` 时，重复项按相反顺序处理："

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.df_nsmallest:78 of
msgid "When using ``keep='all'``, all duplicate items are maintained:"
msgstr "当使用 ``keep='all'`` 时，所有重复项都会保留："

#: maxframe.dataframe.sort.nsmallest.df_nsmallest:87 of
msgid ""
"To order by the smallest values in column \"population\" and then "
"\"GDP\", we can specify multiple columns like in the next example."
msgstr ""
"要按 \"population\" 列中的最小值排序，然后按 \"GDP\" 排序，可以像下一个"
"示例中那样指定多个列。"

